title: Billa
subTitle: Billa, a notorious gangster, is fatally wounded during an encounter with the police. The police commissioner decides to secretly replace him with a lookalike to help catch his gang.

title: Chinna Veedu
subTitle: Gopal marries Bhagyalakshmi, a plain and unsophisticated woman, at his father's behest. However, when he meets Banu, he gets attracted to her without realising her true motives.

title: Anna Nagar Mudhal Theru
subTitle: Sivaraman, a desperate unemployed youth, disguises himself as a Gorkha and takes up the job of a watchman. However, he is surprised when his childhood sweetheart moves into the colony he works in.

title: Coimbatore Mappillai
subTitle: When Balu moves to the city in search of career opportunities, he falls in love with Sumithra. However, Sumithra's evil cousin, Mahesh, creates a rift between their blooming love.

title: Thavasi
subTitle: Thavasi is a revered landlord who lives in a small village. However, his life changes drastically when a young man commits suicide due to a misjudgement he makes.

title: Vasantha Maligai
subTitle: Latha meets Anand, an alcoholic, when he saves her from getting raped. Thereafter, she gets a job as his secretary and helps change his behaviour, but his toxic family tries to suppress her.

title: Lovely
subTitle: Mahadevan does not believe in love and hates the word, but his daughter Nivedha loves Chandru. In order to get his consent, the couple comes up with an intricate plan and executes it.

title: Ennavale
subTitle: Lakshmi, a landlord's daughter, encourages James, a struggling singer, to gain recognition. However, when James proposes to her, Lakshmi turns him down due to her bitter past.

title: Jhonny
subTitle: Johnny loves Archana, a singer, but their lives are disrupted when Johnny's lookalike kills his lover for infidelity and tries to pin the blame on Johnny. He also takes refuge in Archana's house.

title: Thambikku Entha Ooru
subTitle: Seeing Balu's spendthrift and carefree attitude, his father sends him to his friend's house in a village to get reformed. Things get complicated when he gets entangled in a love triangle.

title: Mr. Bharath
subTitle: A businessman abandons his first love, to marry a rich heiress. However, things take a turn when his illegitimate son seeks revenge for the injustice done to his mother.

title: Gentleman
subTitle: Kicha is a modern-day Robin Hood, who along with his friend, Mani, steals from the rich to aid the poor. In society, he is a respected man who runs a small business.

title: Billa
subTitle: When Billa, a don, dies at the hands of ACP Murthy, he is replaced by Ranga, his lookalike, to infiltrate the gang. When Murthy is killed, Ranga is trapped since only Murthy knew the truth.

title: Kaalam Maari Pochu
subTitle: Indra and her three sisters are married off to mediocre men by their patriarchal father. However, he realises their importance when his son stirs discord in the family.

title: Nayagan
subTitle: A man who witnesses the gruesome murder of his father kills a corrupt policeman and flees to Mumbai to become a gangster.

title: Thooral Ninnu Pochu
subTitle: Two families arrange the marriage of their son and daughter, who fall in love. However, tensions arise when the families clash over dowry demands, leading to the cancellation of the wedding.

title: Vanaja Girija
subTitle: Sisters Vanaja and Girija believe they were abandoned by their father due to the influence of a man named Ramanathan. The duo vow to alienate Ramanathan from his family as he did to theirs.

title: Veettukku Veedu Vasappadi
subTitle: Jagan, a successful doctor, ties the knot with Jaya. However, their marital life becomes increasingly strained due to Jagan's profession.

title: Yai Nee Romba Azhaga Irukke
subTitle: Hari, a young man, is in love with Raji, who does not reciprocate his feelings. Meanwhile, Swapna pursues Hari but is scorned when he rejects her and goes on to harass him.

subTitle: Kanmani plans to teach Chinnamani a lesson by pretending to love him. However, it backfires when he ends up marrying her for vengeance.

subTitle: Inderjeet, a singer, is the primary suspect when his female fans are found murdered by a serial killer. Meanwhile, Divya, the first victim's sister, comes to the city to find the killer.

subTitle: Raja and Ravi, two best friends, fall in love with the same girl, Radha. But, trouble ensues when Ravi expects a sacrifice from her, in order to save his best friend.
